                  <p>Globin variants are given by their conventional nomenclature (<ext-link xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="http://globin.cse.psu.edu/">globin.cse.psu.edu</ext-link>).</p>
