                  <p>Denotes two variations in one allele: deletion of AC at -2 and -3 before ATG initiation codon in <italic toggle="yes">cis</italic> configuration on an -&#x003b1;<sup>3.7</sup> deletion allele [<xref ref-type="bibr" rid="a-thal.REF.viprakasit.2003.133">Viprakasit et al 2003</xref>]</p>
